0.03.name: wordpress/memolane-embedded-timeline-view
0.03.description: This WordPress plugin adds a simple shortcode to embed the awesome Memolane media timeline view in your blog posts and pages. When adding a post with a Memolane embed, first add and configure your lane via the Memolane plugin administrator menu.
